---
title: EVM.loginWithEmail
chain: EVM
---

# `loginWithEmail`
Logs in a user with email and password.

```java
String emailAddress = "email@example.com";
String password = "super-secret-password";

MWEVM.loginWithEmail(emailAddress, password, new MirrorCallback () {
    @Override
    public void callback(String loginRawResult) {
        Log.d("MirrorSDK","login result is" + loginRawResult);
    }
});
```
